    "Clean minimalist layout with consistent form and button styling",
    "Clear empty and error states, including a dismissible alert with actionable copy",
    "Strong visible focus treatment and solid baseline accessibility signals"
  ],
  "top_issues": [
    "Little evidence of preventative validation; the add form uses novalidate and the Add action appears available with an empty field",
    "Limited user control and efficiency features such as undo/cancel, shortcuts, or bulk actions",
    "Loading or busy feedback is subtle and may be easy to miss"
  ]
